-- G6: half-open range pattern `lo..hi` in a match arm.  PRng canonicalizes to
-- PWild in the decision matrix, so the tree routes here unconditionally and the
-- guarded-arm re-match emits `lo <= n && n < hi` (half-open: `n <= hi-1`).
-- Boundaries: 1->digit, 8->digit, 9->big (excluded), 0->big.
-- digit=1, big=0 ; main = 1 + 1 + 0 + 0 = 2
classify n = match n
  1..9 => 1
  _ => 0

main = classify 1 + classify 8 + classify 9 + classify 0
